## Quick Start

```bash
cp .env.example .env
<% if (packageManager === 'yarn') { %>yarn install<% } else if (packageManager === 'pnpm') { %>pnpm install<% } else if (packageManager === 'bun') { %>bun install<% } else { %>npm install<% } %>
<% if (packageManager === 'yarn') { %>yarn prisma:migrate<% } else if (packageManager === 'pnpm') { %>pnpm run prisma:migrate<% } else if (packageManager === 'bun') { %>bun run prisma:migrate<% } else { %>npm run prisma:migrate<% } %>
<% if (packageManager === 'yarn') { %>yarn start:dev<% } else if (packageManager === 'pnpm') { %>pnpm run start:dev<% } else if (packageManager === 'bun') { %>bun run start:dev<% } else { %>npm run start:dev<% } %>
```

Health check: `GET /health`

## Add Auth

```bash
zimt auth
```

## Generate Endpoints

```bash
# From a name
zimt generate products

# From SQL
zimt generate create "CREATE TABLE orders (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, total DECIMAL NOT NULL)"
```

